{"tid":2392063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上上下堂成地都係玻璃碎","createTime":"2021-02-02T14:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T14:58:29.000Z","uid":113234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b17a062664f2080a32a5ff5cd1ed9b53ccfcce7","tid":2392063,"uid":113234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟讀緊一科關於可持續發展嘅科<br />\n<br />\n咁今堂呀sir就探討香港如何可以達致可持續發展<br />\n<br />\n突然間有個同學就係chat room 到提出「源頭減人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係唔比走腥港人落黎<br />\n<br />\n點知呢句就觸動到一班NDS嘅弱小心靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好笑係叫人認識國安法先好出聲<br />\n<br />\n以下hide左名嘅係local student<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqZfThg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqZfThg.jpg&h=a584977c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykP0jXh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykP0jXh.jpg&h=e0ed40e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNJz8QC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNJz8QC.jpg&h=e2b13757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Z19XJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Z19XJY.jpg&h=1456f641&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuOTEXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuOTEXi.jpg&h=08c9a56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大致上都係一貫小粉紅嘅理論：<br />\n<br />\n1. 大劣益左好多野比香港<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港至古以來都是中国的<br />\n<br />\n3. 咁唔中意你咪走囉<br />\n<br />\n4. 香港用的電是中国的電，飲的都是中国的水<br />\n<br />\n然後個sir扮睇唔到繼續講書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日讀書真係慘<br />\n<br />\n明明理性討論都可以比人上綱上線"},{"pid":"dd19fd7c3e9952b0825fe912b7919c80526c701f","tid":2392063,"uid":283704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dcf67bdb7ee5767f42b54c3226957985188891","tid":2392063,"uid":143260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意中國又過嚟香港讀書<br />\n咁撚屌成日講又講到中國咁撚勁但又唔彈返去清華讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f36f2fdf7714d66a11482fb0425574b01ecde7","tid":2392063,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"任何討論 只要有中國人出現<br />\n你就知道 這個討論將會失焦 無限放大<br />\n和突顯中國人的矛盾心態"},{"pid":"20ce9c7052f53d1cfce28d0c375c1ca4c41b6dc6","tid":2392063,"uid":181217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"香港人就係二等公民"}]}